# Vendor-specific AI infrastructure — personal / per-machine runtime state.
#
# IMPORTANT: this repo deliberately tracks AI *steering* files — CLAUDE.md,
# GEMINI.md, AGENTS.md, .cursorrules, .windsurfrules,
# .github/copilot-instructions.md — and the templates/ that ship them. Those are
# the product and must stay tracked. Only the personal runtime/IDE directories and
# local history/caches below are ignored (the "infrastructure", not the steering).
#
# The shared skills layer (agent-skills/) is likewise TRACKED. The runtime dirs below
# also hold local, regenerated skill *adapters* (.claude/skills/, .gemini/commands/,
# .cursor/rules/) — local-only; the neutral agent-skills/ is the shared source of truth.

# Agent / AI-IDE runtime directories
.kiro/
.claude/
.cursor/
.continue/
.windsurf/
.codeium/
.gemini/
.cline/
.roo/
.zed/
.codex/

# Aider local history / cache (steering files like .aider.conf.yml stay tracked)
.aider.chat.history.md
.aider.input.history
.aider.tags.cache*

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
